    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like he's waiting for me. i have this recurring thought that maybe we weren't meant to be apart. like, what's the point of even trying to \"heal\" when the only person i want to talk to is gone? everything feels so much more peaceful when i just imagine being with him again.",
